                <L-4 L="EN">This service is a cyclic main function to check for new received frames in polling mode.</L-4>
              </LONG-NAME>
              <DESC>
                <L-2 L="EN">The function checks for new received frames in polling mode for the FIFO EthCtrlConfigIngressFifo belonging to the EthCtrl EthernetCommunicationController. </L-2>
              </DESC>
